<HEADLINE>
FT  22 DEC 93 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1993
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CHRISTOPHER PRICE, PETER JOHN and STEVE THOMPSON
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (252)
BRITISH FUNDS (1) AMERICANS (1) BANKS (1) Royal Bank of Scotland, BREWERS
(5) Allied-Lyons, Gibbs Mew, Greenalls, Matthew Clark, Whitbread, BLDG MATLS
(14) BPB, Blockleys, Caradon, Do. Pf., Grafton, Hepworth, Heywood Williams
Pf., Ibstock Johnsen, Marley, Pilkingtom, Do. Wrrts., Shaw (A), Sheffield
Ins., Tarmac, BUSINESS SERVS (1) Hays, CHEMS (1) Laporte, CONGLOMERATES (2)
Daimler Benz, Sime Darby, CONTG &amp; CONSTRCN (12) Berkeley, Bett Bros.,
Bryant, Maunders (J), McAlpine (A), McCarthy &amp; Stone, Prowting, Sheriff, Tay
Homes, Westbury, Wilson Bowden, Wilson (C), ELECTRICALS (1) Oxford Ins.,
ELECTRICITY (1) Natl. Power, ELECTRONICS (9) Control Tech.,
Electrocomponents, Farnell, Phonelink, Rodime, Roxboro, Siemans, Soundtracs,
Virtuality, ENG GEN (10) Bullough, Clyde Blowers, FKI, GBE, Halma, Hill &amp;
Smith, IMI, Protean, TI, Vickers, FOOD MANUF (4) Assoc. Brit. Foods, Cadbury
Schweppes, Kakuzi, Nestle, FOOD RETAILING (1) Park, HEALTH &amp; HSEHOLD (3)
