   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   HAMBURG
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The German cocoa buyers' umbrella organisation Kakao-Einkaufs-Gesellschaft
is encouraging processors to take advantage of cheap cocoa following the
recent price slump, reports Reuter from Hamburg.
