FT  22 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Faupel slips to Pounds 404,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Faupel Trading, the USM-quoted textile importer, returned pre-tax profits of
Pounds 404,000 for the half year ended September 30, down 37 per cent on
last time's Pounds 639,000.
The result was 'somewhat below' directors' initial expectations and the
shares slipped 9p to 80p.
