and garments for Pounds 6.55m (Pounds 7.59m).
There were lower earnings per share of 2.87p (5.19p). The interim dividend
is a same-again 1.85p.
The directors said an office had been established in Shanghai which would
enable the group to keep abreast of the 'rapidly developing' supply base in
China.
